    "description": "本应用是《玩个Gui》的免费序章版本，玩家可以玩到游戏的前两个阶段，组建合理且强大的回路来抵御每一波怪海的攻击。<br><br><strong>全新的序章版本</strong><br>序章将开放60-80分钟的游戏内容。<br>在序章中，玩家可以体验到游戏正式版的核心内容。<br><br><strong>全新的战车</strong><br>旧版本的战车已经全部拆分重做，14种全新的战车将在序章中登场~<br><br><strong>全新Boss袭来</strong><br>2个全新的BOSS带着他们的爪牙在序章袭来！<br><br><strong>序章Demo专属成就</strong><br>我们为序章和Demo试玩版设计了4个独特成就，欢迎玩家们来挑战和获取它们！<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >铺设轨道 激活元素领域</h2></strong><br>自由连接基站，设计你的多重防守线路，激活元素场域，伤害与干扰敌人。<br>但请注意这是家园的最后防线，离主基地太远可能会有不好的事情发生……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/0ed35913043a382fe5cd70e0bf929080.poster.avif?t=1727370808\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/0ed35913043a382fe5cd70e0bf929080.webm?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/0ed35913043a382fe5cd70e0bf929080.mp4?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级车列  碾压无穷怪海</h2></strong><br>玩家将拥有无比强大的车列战斗体系。让各条车列在激烈的战役中迅速成长，满屏的枪火导弹、冰霜火海、电闪雷鸣，特效越帅杀敌越快！碾压这群敢来送死的渣渣们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/8435d0270bd6dbdf7152294584812ed2.poster.avif?t=1727370808\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/8435d0270bd6dbdf7152294584812ed2.webm?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/8435d0270bd6dbdf7152294584812ed2.mp4?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由组合  探索全新武器机制</h2></strong><br>机枪战车、导弹战车、连连战车两两组合、魅力无限，还有更多隐藏武器等你发掘合成，每局都是从未见过的船新版本。<br>1+1&gt;2？1+1+1+1+1+1+……当然是无限大！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/218d6db45f60d0ee53d1bb30444b0c9e.poster.avif?t=1727370808\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/218d6db45f60d0ee53d1bb30444b0c9e.webm?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065690/extras/218d6db45f60d0ee53d1bb30444b0c9e.mp4?t=1727370808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
